textAnnotations.description:
2018 PTTSBURGH POST-GAZㅌ TTE
CREATORS SYNDICATE
BLACK FRIDAY
CYBER MONDAY
AND GIVING TUESDAY
JAMMED OUR EMAIL
WITH SOLICITATIONS/
SO TODAY IS
UNSUBSCRIBE
WEDNESDAY...
IP
Copygnt by Steve Keley
